    </h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Primary Accents</h3>
        <div class="p-6 rounded bg-primary-500 text-white">
          <p class="font-mono text-sm">primary-500</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 rounded bg-primary-600 text-white">
          <p class="font-mono text-sm">primary-600</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 rounded bg-primary-700 text-white">
